cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques applied to radiology reports, which falls under the scope of cs.CL.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a machine learning approach to estimate label uncertainty, which falls under the scope of cs.LG.
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper discusses downstream image model training, which is related to computer vision and pattern recognition, falling under the scope of cs.CV.
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes an AI-based approach to improve the efficiency of image models, which falls under the scope of cs.AI.
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with parsing radiology reports, which can be considered a form of information retrieval, falling under the scope of cs.IR.
